### User API Examples
### Base URL: https://localhost:7000/api/user

### 1. Get all users
GET https://localhost:7000/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get user by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Create a new user (Lead)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@example.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "type": "Lead"
}

###

### 4. Create a new user (Customer)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Santos",
  "email": "maria.santos@example.com",
  "password": "senha456",
  "type": "Customer"
}

###

### 5. Update user
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "email": "joao.silva.novo@example.com",
  "password": "novaSenha123",
  "type": "Customer"
}

###

### 6. Delete user
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 7. Test validation - Invalid email
POST https://localhost:7000/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "senha123",
  "type": "Lead"
}

